sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI as Logs
    participant Docker as DockerManager
    participant Container

    User->>CLI: orbit logs orbit-php-83
    CLI->>Docker: logs(container, follow)
    Docker->>Container: docker logs -f
    loop streaming
        Container-->>Docker: log lines
        Docker-->>CLI: output
        CLI-->>User: display logs
    end
    User->>CLI: Ctrl+C
    CLI-->>User: stopped
